<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Movie Database</title>
	<style>
		body {
			background-color: #f7f7f7;
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			color: #444;
		}

		h1 {
			color: #0085a1;
			font-size: 36px;
			margin-top: 50px;
			text-align: center;
			text-shadow: 1px 1px #eee;
		}

		p {
			font-size: 24px;
			margin: 50px auto;
			max-width: 800px;
			text-align: center;
		}

		button {
			background-color: #0085a1;
			border: none;
			border-radius: 5px;
			color: #fff;
			cursor: pointer;
			font-size: 18px;
			padding: 10px 20px;
			text-shadow: 1px 1px #333;
			transition: background-color 0.3s;
		}

			button:hover {
				background-color: #004f5e;
			}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<h1>Welcome to the Movie Database</h1>
	<p>This is a movie database where you can add and view movies, artists, directors, comments, and ratings.</p>
	<form action="/movies" style="text-align: center;">
		<button type="submit">Get Access to the MovieList</button>
	</form>
</body>
</html>
